            </p>
          </section>
          <section class="section-container--block" aria-labelledby="footerCreditsHeader">
            <h2 class="text-h3" id="footerCreditsHeader">
              Produced by
            </h2>
            <div class="section-container--block">
              <h3 class="image-title landscape">
                <img
                  src="<%= image_path "codenewbie_logo.png", resize: "320" %>"
                  width="1252"
                  height="183"
                  alt="CodeNewbie"
                  sizes="(min-width: 260px) 320px,  calc((100vw - 2em)"
                  srcset="
                  <%= image_path "codenewbie_logo.png", resize: "320" %> 320w,
                  <%= image_path "codenewbie_logo.png", resize: "640" %> 640w,
                  <%= image_path "codenewbie_logo.png", resize: "960" %> 960w,
                  "
                >
              </h3>
              <p>
                <a href="https://www.codenewbie.org/" target="_blank">CodeNewbie</a>
                is the most supportive community of programmers and people learning
                to code. We produce content to support people on their coding
