              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="section-container--block">
              <h3 class="image-title square">
                <img
                  src="<%= image_path "DEV-tilted.png", resize: "80" %>"
                  width="80"
                  height="80"
                  alt="DEV"
                  sizes="80px"
                  srcset="
                  <%= image_path "DEV-tilted.png", resize: "80" %> 80w,
                  <%= image_path "DEV-tilted.png", resize: "160" %> 160w,
                  <%= image_path "DEV-tilted.png", resize: "240" %> 240w,
                  "
                >
              </h3>
              <p>
                <a href="https://dev.to" target="_blank">DEV</a> is a
                community of software developers getting together to help one
                another out. The software industry relies on collaboration and
                networked learning. We provide a place for that to happen.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
        <nav class="footer-body--contact" aria-labelledby="footerContactLinks">
          <h2 class="text-h3" id="footerContactLinks">
            Contact
          </h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Twitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/CodeNewbies" target="_blank">@CodeLandConf</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              Email: <a href="mailto:hello@forem.com" target="_blank">hello@forem.com</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
        <nav class="footer-body--links" aria-label="Legal Information">
          <ul>
            <li>
              <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
